description: Adds one or more tags to the specified resource.

parameters.name: ResourceARN
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the resource that you want to retrieve tags for.

parameters.name: Tags
parameters.description: The tags to add to the specified resource. Specifying the tag key is required. You can set the value of a tag to an empty string, but you can't set the value of a tag to null. (dict) --- A custom key-value pair that's associated with a resource. The key identifier, or name, of the tag. The string value that's associated with the key of the tag. You can set the value of a tag to an empty string, but you can't set the value of a tag to null.

nested_params.name: Key
nested_params.description: The key identifier, or name, of the tag.

nested_params.name: Value
nested_params.description: The string value that's associated with the key of the tag. You can set the value of a tag to an empty string, but you can't set the value of a tag to null.
